376
00:32:48,070 --> 00:32:48,610
Of course.

377
00:32:48,750 --> 00:32:49,650
If it was the accident

378
00:32:49,650 --> 00:32:51,050
that caused the trauma,

379
00:32:51,070 --> 00:32:52,530
it would be easy and clear to define the responsibilities.

380
00:32:52,990 --> 00:32:55,030
But what caused his unconsciousness first,

381
00:32:55,070 --> 00:32:56,060
the accident or his illness itself,

382
00:32:56,060 --> 00:32:57,350
the real reason means totally different results to our company.

383
00:32:58,580 --> 00:33:00,330
Same with your company, right?

384
00:33:12,430 --> 00:33:14,380
Actually, you could have asked for leave.

385
00:33:15,280 --> 00:33:16,790
