504
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:26,760
Sometimes she can, sometimes she can't.

505
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:27,480
Greet her.

506
00:41:29,650 --> 00:41:30,700
Hello, Granny Zeng Jiang.

507
00:41:33,030 --> 00:41:34,430
I was just joking.

508
00:41:34,710 --> 00:41:36,570
How can you say she couldn't rest in peace?

509
00:41:37,460 --> 00:41:38,830
