516
00:41:49,620 --> 00:41:50,450
With an ink brush, of course.

517
00:41:50,480 --> 00:41:51,190
What else can I use?

518
00:41:51,610 --> 00:41:52,240
It's used.

519
00:41:52,990 --> 00:41:54,500
I washed it.

520
00:41:55,510 --> 00:41:56,660
When grandpa comes back,

521
00:41:56,820 --> 00:41:57,560
I'll write one for him too.

522
00:41:58,500 --> 00:41:59,080
No.

523
00:41:59,480 --> 00:42:00,170
He'll get poisoned.

524
00:42:01,570 --> 00:42:02,880
Eat up.

525
00:42:03,200 --> 00:42:04,240
