536
00:42:38,590 --> 00:42:39,350
No, I didn't.

537
00:42:40,240 --> 00:42:41,910
I kept my eyes closed.

538
00:42:41,910 --> 00:42:42,870
I saw nothing.

539
00:42:42,900 --> 00:42:43,480
Happy?

540
00:42:49,390 --> 00:42:50,280
