543
00:42:54,250 --> 00:42:55,740
Go back and finish high school.

544
00:42:56,500 --> 00:42:58,040
It doesn't matter if I don't.

545
00:42:58,330 --> 00:42:59,680
It's just a graduation certificate.

546
00:43:00,130 --> 00:43:00,970
Do you think I just want you

547
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:02,060
to get your graduation certificate?

548
00:43:03,710 --> 00:43:04,910
I don't want you

549
00:43:05,090 --> 00:43:07,260
