550
00:43:10,080 --> 00:43:10,520
No.

551
00:43:11,360 --> 00:43:12,210
I've had plans.

552
00:43:15,920 --> 00:43:17,200
I have no plans at all.

553
00:43:19,540 --> 00:43:20,850
But how could I go back

554
00:43:20,880 --> 00:43:22,190
and hide in high school to be a student?

555
00:43:23,270 --> 00:43:24,230
What if they won't pay

556
00:43:24,260 --> 00:43:25,450
for grandpa's medical expensesï¼Ÿ

